<T>__{cut to:}
<B>__{inigo}
<A>__{and behind him now, drawing closer all the time, is the deadly edge of the cliffs of insanity. inigo fights and ducks and feints and slashes and it all works, but not for long, as gradually the man in black keeps the advantage, keeps forcing inigo back, closer and closer to death.}
<C>__{inigo}
<P>__{(happy as a clam)}
<D>__{you are wonderful!}
<C>__{man in black}
<D>__{thank you i've worked hard to become so.}
<A>__{the cliff edge is very close now. inigo is continually being forced toward it.}
<C>__{inigo}
<D>__{i admit it you are better than i am.}
<C>__{man in black}
<D>__{then why are you smiling?}
<A>__{inches from defeat, inigo is, in fact, all smiles.}
<C>__{inigo}
<D>__{because i know something you don't know.}
<C>__{man in black}
<D>__{and what is that?}
<C>__{inigo}
